  "name": "RPlog_Angry_Rancor_Deal_Pt_II",
  "title": "Angry Rancor Deal (Part II)",
  "summary": "In the quiet pre-evening hours of the Angry Rancor's casino, Commander Imriel and his two Imperial aides finalize the terms of their arrangement with the Jordain sisters who run the cruise ship. Imriel exchanges cordial introductions and farewells with the visiting Captain Bruno before settling into the lounge with Inanna and her flamboyant sister Serenella, who insists on being called Sel. Over a round of waters that Serenella mockingly teases the Imperials for ordering, the entertainer flirts shamelessly with Imriel's young lieutenants while Inanna keeps the conversation on business -- port-of-call listings and the practicalities of the deal. Imriel allows his men their fun within reason as he and Inanna confirm that the Marshal is pleased and that all concerns have been addressed. The delegation finishes their drinks, straightens their uniforms, and rises to depart, Serenella beaming her goodbyes and Inanna offering a respectful, almost-bowing nod as the deal is brought to a satisfactory close.",
